 min's to get this stupid hammer to proc. Though once you have it it will put a smile on your face when you're stuck somewhere and get a free ride home, I've had mine since lvl 53 and have loved it ever since. <br>11. The hammer is giant so you'll need a bag that can handle it <br>Happy hunting <br>Faehan &lt;68 bst of kane bayle&gt;<br></p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >0 Replies</td></tr></table>
